VEighty-six percent of human societies permit a man to have several wives:
p17
aVpolygyny.
p18
aVBut in the vast majority of these cultures,
p19
aVonly about five or ten percent of men actually do have several wives.
p20
aVHaving several partners can be a toothache.
p21
aVIn fact, co-wives can fight with each other,
p22
aVsometimes they can even poison each other's children.
