aVAnd I've long ago maintained
p47
aVthat we've evolved three distinctly different brain systems
p48
aVfor mating and reproduction:
p49
aVsex drive,
p50
aVfeelings of intense romantic love
p51
aVand feelings of deep cosmic attachment to a long-term partner.
